neat

Class InnovationDatabase

  • java.lang.Object
    • neat.InnovationDatabase

  • public class InnovationDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
    Provides the NEAT innovation database as described in Kenneth Stanley's NEAT papers The innovations are kept for the entire life of the run.
    Author:
    MSimmerson (NEAT4J)

        NEATChromosome createTemplate(int inputs,
                              int outputs,
                              java.util.Hashtable<java.lang.String,XMLFieldEntry> properties,
                              java.util.Random rand)
        Parameters:
        featureSelection - - if true assigns one connection to each output to a random input. If false, all inputs are connected to all outputs
        extraFeatureCount - - creates chromosome features that are non structural, ie they have no bearing on the creation of the net they represent evolving data inputs.
